ource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group of three which included Stadelmann, a European bronze medallist, and Marin was a tough draw for Darragh, whose singles campaign is now over.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To embed this post, copy the code below on your site  600px wide<iframe width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0px;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.the42.ie/https://www.the42.ie/rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024/?embedpost=6451374&width=600&height=460\\\" ></iframe>  400px wide<iframe width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0px;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.the42.ie/https://www.the42.ie/rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024/?embedpost=6451374&width=400&height=460\\\" ></iframe>  300px wide<iframe width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border:0px;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.the42.ie/https://www.the42.ie/rachel-darragh-olympics-6451374-Jul2024/?embedpost=6451374&width=300&height=460\\\" ></iframe>  Access to the comments facility has been disabled for this user  Create an email alert based on the current article\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}]}"